Chart #1, Thomas French, 1584
Assington, Suffolk, England
and various other families

This page was updated by Mara French on 9/1/12. Send any corrections or additions to this chart to marafrench@mindspring.com.

Almost 5,956 Frenches included here. This index was compiled dated July 2006 and is to be used for reference only. The links are not updated in this file, and therefore the links may be broken. If you see a name listed below that youd like further info on, please go directly to the updated index on Chart #1 which is on another web server. The index below will help you in the future when a search tool is added to the FFA website.
